### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Ingest a document (update the file path before running)
POST http://localhost:8000/ingest?doc_type=work_order
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample_data/sample.pdf
--boundary--

### Ask the copilot (semantic question)
POST http://localhost:8000/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What does the SOP say about lockout-tagout for V-204A?",
  "top_k": 8
}

### Ask the copilot (relationship / graph question)
POST http://localhost:8000/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Which pumps have failed more than twice this year and what were the root causes?",
  "top_k": 8
}

### Load an equipment neighborhood from the graph
GET http://localhost:8000/graph/neighborhood?entity_id=P-101&depth=2
